<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.10">
<l>poṉṉumā maṇiyum muttamuñ cumantu porutirai mānati puṭaicūḻn</l>
<l>taṉṉamā ṭulavu malaipuṉal cūḻnta varaṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉai</l>
<l>maṉṉumā māṭa maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ māṉavēṟ kaliyaṉvā yolikaḷ</l>
<l>paṉṉiya paṉuval pāṭuvār nāḷum paḻaviṉai paṟṟaṟup pārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who daily sing this composition written in verse by Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a spear of renown,</l>
<l>Chief of those of Maṅkai with sturdy, great mansions,</l>
<l rend="indent">about the one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam</l>
<l>Surrounded by billowing water where swans glide at the sides,</l>
<l rend="indent">being surrounded on [all] sides by a great river with dashing waves</l>
<l>Carrying gold, great jewels, and pearls,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will sever the bonds of former fate.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
